description=Pink tint fix for Exynos 9611 (A51/M21/M31/F41). Patches SGCAM DEX for AsShotNeutral=1 1 1, configurable black level, AWB bypass, and preview lag fixes. Tribute to TBM13 for the Exynos camera library patches and pink-tint diagnosis (issue #23). By thunderoar.
